text: Kati Psinete (Greek: Κάτι Ψήνεται) (meaning Something's cooking) is a popular cookery show. It's the Greek edition of the show Come Dine With Me (UK). It began airing on Alpha TV on March 30, 2009 for 8 seasons. From January 7, 2019 it broadcasting on ANT1 TV and is continuing today with great success, according to AGB. ==External links== * Category:Alpha TV original programming Category:2009 Greek television series debuts Category:Cooking television series Category:2000s Greek television series Category:2010s Greek television series Come Dine
